<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>269</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw Pathian, thihnak tei in, Vancung kalmi, Na dawt Fapa Jesuh ca-ah
 kan in thangthat.

[C1]
   Hal-le-lu-jah, Lianhngan, sunpar; Hal-le-lu-jah, Amen!
   Hal-le-lu-jah, Nang ta kan si, Kan nunter than tuah.

[V2]
 Maw Pathian, nangmah ceunak Thlarau ca-ah, Khamhbawi a kan hmuhsak
 ca-ah kan in thangthat.

[C2]
   Hal-le-lu-jah, Lianhngan, sunpar; Hal-le-lu-jah, Amen!
   Hal-le-lu-jah, Nang ta kan si, Kan nunter than tuah.

[V3]
 Thah ciami Tuufa,sunpar thangthat si seh, Kan sual vialte phortu le a
 kan thiantertu.

[C3]
   Hal-le-lu-jah, Lianhngan, sunpar; Hal-le-lu-jah, Amen!
   Hal-le-lu-jah, Nang ta kan si, Kan nunter than tuah.

[V4]
 Kan nunter than law, Na dawtnak sung bik le, Na vancung mei in, kan
 lung chung hi alhter ko.

[C4]
   Hal-le-lu-jah, Lianhngan, sunpar; Hal-le-lu-jah, Amen!
   Hal-le-lu-jah, Nang ta kan si, Kan nunter than tuah.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>KAN NUNTER THAN CH269</title>
</song>